----------------------------------------------------------------------

WHY GPLv3 (AND NOT A PERMISSIVE LICENCE)

This Swift engine is a derivative work of 'Johnny Reborn' (jc_reborn),
the C/SDL2 engine by Jeremie Guillaume, which is licensed GPLv3-or-later.
Large parts of this codebase — in particular the TTM bytecode interpreter,
the ADS/scene scheduler, and the walk/path-finding logic and its data
tables — were translated function-by-function from jc_reborn's source
(see the per-file "Translated from ..." headers and the Acknowledgements
section of README.md). Under the GPL, the combined work must therefore be
distributed under the GPL. The permissive licence this project previously
carried was not a licence the author was entitled to grant, and has been
corrected to GPLv3-or-later to match upstream.

----------------------------------------------------------------------

SCOPE — SOURCE CODE ONLY

This licence covers ONLY the source code in this repository: the Swift
engine, renderer, parser, debug app, and screensaver bundle.

It does NOT cover the original Sierra/Dynamix "Johnny Castaway" data files
(RESOURCE.MAP, RESOURCE.001, sound*.wav, sprite art, scripts), which remain
the intellectual property of their respective rightsholders. This repository
contains no Sierra data and distributes none. Users supply their own data
files; see README.md for details.
